General.Name: Crypto-X
General.Description:
Crypto – X is a decentralized peer-to-peer gateway that connects Planet Earth to Cryptographic Digital Assetization. Operating on the Ethereum Blockchain, Crypto – X will develop a fully functional encrypted basic income generating system for low-wage citizens to join.

Utilizing the Crypto – X protocol, users are able to hold, transfer, and earn their collective financial assets in a decentral monetized digital centre (crypto-currency wallet) that is fully encrypted beyond the control of financial restrains.

CWX is an ERC20 token that powers Crypto-X' protocol.

Crypto-X will be holding its ICO on December 25th, 2017. The ICO token supply represents 68% of the total token supply, so there will be a total of 13,833,333 tokens available, for a starting price of  0.0001 ETH each at the offering. The ICO funding target is 200 ETH, the funding cap is 1,340 ETH and is expected to end on January 25th, 2017 or when the funding cap is reached.

Token Reserve Split (32%):

  • 5% Team;
  • 1% Bounty program;
  • 26% register CWX token holders;

Crypto-X ICO campaign will feature Bounties, Escrow service, and the token will not be mineable.
